## Guard dialogue
You can convince the guard, either by a persuasion, or a strength check to let you into the tavern. It sets a flag `PTM_TechSkillcheck_GuardPersuasionSuccess`, which triggers an Osiris script `GuardPersuasionButtonUnlock`, that utilizes `PROC_ItemUnlockAndOpen` to unlock the door and open it. After either success or failure it also sets a flag `PTM_TechSkillcheck_GuardAfterDialogue`, which prevents dialogue from repeating and instead plays just a different greeting.

## Pickpocketing 
The guard has a key to the tavern in his inventory which can be pickpocketed from him.

